org.apps8os.trafficsense.util

Class Email

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apps8os.trafficsense.util.Email

  • public class Email
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple data container for a email. Recognizes that e-mails have a sender, a send time, a subject, and content. Provides methods to set and get these parts.

    Jussi
